etomica.chem.elements

Class ElementChemical

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.chem.elements.Element
      • etomica.chem.elements.ElementChemical
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IElement, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Argon, Carbon, Chlorine, Copper, Fluoride, Helium, Hydrogen, HydrogenP, Nitrogen, Oxygen, Silver, Sodium, Sulfur, Tin, Tungsten

    public class ElementChemical
extends Element
    Abstract structure for a class defining one of the chemical elements. Subclasses are (or will be) defined to correspond to each element in the periodic table.
